e_content">                        <div id = "message_header">                            How  to Sponsor                        </div>                        <div id = "message_text">                            <p>As the Directors of Business Relations for the 18th session of UC Berkeley’s Model United Nations conference (UCBMUN XVIII), we are delighted to inform you of a sponsorship opportunity for your organization.</p>                            <p>UC Berkeley Model United Nations (UCBMUN) is an annual conference hosted in the heart of San Francisco by the UC Berkeley Model UN Club. This year, UCBMUN will be held from 6th-9th March, 2014 and will host students from top universities from across the nation including Harvard University, Stanford University, University of Pennsylvania to name a few. Overall, we expect over 500 bright delegates and 100 staff members, each searching for internships, jobs, and educational opportunities. we can guarantee that your institution will find an appropriate audience in our participants.</p>                            <p>Past sponsors of UCBMUN include multinational companies like Lufthansa and prestigious educational institutions such as Boston University’s International Relations department, Columbia University’s School of International and Public Affairs, among others. Your organization’s contribution will allow UCBMUN to continue to meet its aspirations of hosting a world-class annual conference that brings together future world leaders and educates them to create positive change in the world of tomorrow. With our new innovative sponsorship packages, almost anyone can sponsor UCBMUN XVIII, and every organization is guaranteed a return on their investment through creating new networks with potential employees, finding prospective customers and building on your organization’s image and outreach.</p>                            <p>Attached to the right is our Sponsorship Packet, which highlights the goals of UCBMUN X